OL,3,CSoftware provider facing #6m fine over
OL,4,Cransomware attack that hit NHS services
OL,6,FThe firm provides IT and software
OL,7,Fservices to organisations around the
OL,8,Fcountry, including the NHS and other
OL,9,Fhealth providers, handling information
OL,10,Fas part of its role as a data
OL,11,Fprocessor.
OL,13,FIn August 2022, hackers accessed a
OL,14,Fnumber of the firm's health and care
OL,15,Fsystems via a customer account which
OL,16,Fdid not have multi-factor
OL,17,Fauthentication.
