OL,3,CSoftware provider facing #6m fine over
OL,4,Cransomware attack that hit NHS services
OL,6,FThe attack led to disruption to
OL,7,Fcritical services including NHS 111,
OL,8,Fand data taken included phone numbers
OL,9,Fand medical records, as well as
OL,10,Fdetails on how to gain entry to the
OL,11,Fhomes of nearly 900 people receiving
OL,12,Fcare at home.
OL,14,F"This incident shows just how
OL,15,Fimportant it is to prioritise
OL,16,Finformation security," Information
OL,17,FCommissioner John Edwards said.
