OL,3,CSoftware provider facing #6m fine over
OL,4,Cransomware attack that hit NHS services
OL,6,F"Losing control of sensitive personal
OL,7,Finformation will have been distressing
OL,8,Ffor people who had no choice but to
OL,9,Fput their trust in health and care
OL,10,Forganisations.
OL,12,F"Not only was personal information
OL,13,Fcompromised, but we have also seen
OL,14,Freports that this incident caused
OL,15,Fdisruption to some health services,
OL,16,Fdisrupting their ability to deliver
OL,17,Fpatient care.
OL,19,F"A sector already under pressure was
OL,20,Fput under further strain due to this
OL,21,Fincident.
