OL,3,CSoftware provider facing #6m fine over
OL,4,Cransomware attack that hit NHS services
OL,6,F"For an organisation trusted to handle
OL,7,Fa significant volume of sensitive and
OL,8,Fspecial category data, we have
OL,9,Fprovisionally found serious failings
OL,10,Fin its approach to information
OL,11,Fsecurity prior to this incident.
OL,13,F"Despite already installing measures
OL,14,Fon its corporate systems, our
OL,15,Fprovisional finding is that Advanced
OL,16,Ffailed to keep its healthcare systems
OL,17,Fsecure.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
