OL,3,CSoftware provider facing #6m fine over
OL,4,Cransomware attack that hit NHS services
OL,6,F"We expect all organisations to take
OL,7,Ffundamental steps to secure their
OL,8,Fsystems, such as regularly checking
OL,9,Ffor vulnerabilities, implementing
OL,10,Fmulti-factor authentication and
OL,11,Fkeeping systems up to date with the
OL,12,Flatest security patches.
OL,14,F"I am choosing to publicise this
OL,15,Fprovisional decision today as it is my
OL,16,Fduty to ensure other organisations
OL,17,Fhave information that can help them to
OL,18,Fsecure their systems and avoid similar
OL,19,Fincidents in the future.
