OL,6,F"I urge all organisations, especially
OL,7,Fthose handling sensitive health data,
OL,8,Fto urgently secure external
OL,9,Fconnections with multi-factor
OL,10,Fauthentication."
OL,12,FThe ICO said its findings were
OL,13,Fprovisional and no conclusion should
OL,14,Fyet be drawn on whether there had been
OL,15,Fa breach of data protection law.
OL,17,FThe regulator said it would consider
OL,18,Fany representations from Advanced
OL,19,Fbefore making any final decision on
OL,20,Fthe issue.
